Company Overview












































MISSION STATEMENT


To deliver a competitive and sustainable rate of return to shareholders by exploring for oil and gas resources vital to the world's energy needs.






PetroTerra Corp (OTCQB: PTRA) is a publicly traded oil and gas exploration and development company based in Colorado Springs, Colorado. The company is engaged in identifying, evaluating, and developing early-stage onshore oil and gas opportunities in North America. Our strategy is to focus on assets that are located in high-potential, proven basins that can reduce the geological risks involved in exploration projects.
Our current focus is the Sevier and Beaver Oil Prospects in Utah’s Central Thrust Belt. The Sevier and Beaver Oil Prospects could offer attractive oil discovery within the Navajo Sandstone as the initial target in this high potential proven basin.
Overseeing the development of an oil field from prospects to profits requires a knowledgeable, experienced, and strategic leadership team capable of delivering results. PetroTerra has assembled the human talent necessary to execute this goal.


Learn more about our Leadership
  































